To install this package: cd into the root directory of the package and type:
 > mkdir _build
 > cd _build
 > cmake [options] ..
 > make install

Options can be
  -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=prefix: (default prefix=/usr/local) to set a non
   standard installation prefix,
  -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=[Debug|Release] to build in debug or release  mode,
  -DHPP_DEBUG=True to trigger hpp-util logging and debug machinery.
